div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Övriga</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040067\" data-text=\"zolpidem:missbruk\"></a>Zolpidem, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040068\" data-text=\"zopiklon:missbruk\"></a>zopiklon, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040069\" data-text=\"zaleplon:missbruk\"></a>zale-</div><div class=\"tableLine\">plon, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040071\" data-text=\"klometiazol:missbruk\"></a>klometiazol</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3. Central-</span></div><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;stimulantia<span class=\"tab\"></span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1043644\" data-text=\"amfetamin:missbruk\"></a>Amfetamin, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043645\" data-text=\"metamfetamin:missbruk\"></a>metamfetamin, <br></div><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1043647\" data-text=\"fenmetrazin:missbruk\"></a>fenmetrazin, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043649\" data-text=\"metylfenidat:missbruk\"></a>metylfenidat,<a class=\"index\" id=\"1043650\" data-text=\"efedrin:missbruk\"></a> <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043651\" data-text=\"ecstasy\"></a></div><div class=\"tableLine\">ecstasy (MDMA), <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043652\" data-text=\"khat\"></a>khat (<a class=\"index\" id=\"1043653\" data-text=\"qat\"></a>quat, </div><div class=\"tableLine\">qat, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043654\" data-text=\"tschat\"></a>tschat, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1043655\" data-text=\"miraa\"></a>miraa)</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">4. Kokain</span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040090\" data-text=\"kokain\"></a>Kokain, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040091\" data-text=\"crack;krack\"></a>crack, ”free-base”</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">5. <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040094\" data-text=\"cannabis\"></a>Cannabinoider</span></div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040097\" data-text=\"hasch\"></a>Hasch, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040098\" data-text=\"marijuana\"></a>marijuana</div></td></tr><tr><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">6. Hallucino-</span></div><div class=\"tableLine\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;gener</div></td><td><div class=\"tableLine\"><a class=\"index\" id=\"1040103\" data-text=\"LSD\"></a>LSD, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040104\" data-text=\"meskalin\"></a>meskalin, <a class=\"index\" id=\"1040105\" data-text=\"psilocybin\"></a>psilocybin </div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"footNotes\"><div class=\"tableFootnote\" id=\"fnote_13\">a. <span class=\"tabstop\"></span><div class=\"tableLine\">”Opiater” refererar till narkotiska alkaloider utvunna ur </div><div class=\"tableLine\">opium, såsom t&nbsp;ex morfin och kodein, eller derivat av dessa </div><div class=\"tableLine\">alkaloider, t&nbsp;ex heroin. ”Opioider” refererar till medel som </div><div class=\"tableLine\">inte är opiater, men har liknande farmakologiska effekter, </div><div class=\"tableLine\">t&nbsp;ex syntetiska substanser som ketobemidon, eller endogena </div><div class=\"tableLine\">opioida peptider som enkefalin.</div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>"
